OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss accused staff of
OL,4,Chaving 'hands in the till', inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAnother former Post Office top boss
OL,8,Fhas apologised to sub postmasters for
OL,9,Fthe wrongful convictions, and the
OL,10,Fruined lives and livelihoods as the
OL,11,Finquiry continues, ITV News
OL,12,FCorrespondent Neil Connery reports
OL,14,FA former Post Office boss, who
OL,15,Fclaimed, "subbies" had "their hands in
OL,16,Fthe till" has said he was "unaware"
OL,17,Fthe Post Office was the authority
OL,18,Ftaking sub-postmasters to court.
