OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss accused staff of
OL,4,Chaving 'hands in the till', inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAlan Cook, who was managing director
OL,8,Ffrom 2006-2010, told the Horizon IT
OL,9,Finquiry on Friday that he "was unaware
OL,10,Fthat the Post Office were the
OL,11,Fprosecuting authority".
OL,13,FInstead, he told the government
OL,14,Finquiry, he assumed the "police and
OL,15,FDPP" were the ones taking the sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters to court.
