OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss accused staff of
OL,4,Chaving 'hands in the till', inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FWhile these convictions were being
OL,8,Fhanded out, Mr Cook emailed the Royal
OL,9,FMail Group's PR officer to say he
OL,10,Fthought sub-postmasters "with their
OL,11,Fhand in the till choose to blame the
OL,12,Ftechnology" when cash was missing.
OL,26,@rD@YOUtD@KO]
