OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss accused staff of
OL,4,Chaving 'hands in the till', inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe email, sent in October 2009, said:
OL,8,F"There is a steadily building
OL,9,Fnervousness about the accuracy of the
OL,10,FHorizon system and the press are on it
OL,11,Fnow as well... the system has been
OL,12,Fstable and reliable for many years now
OL,13,Fand there is absolutely no logical
OL,14,Freason why these fears should now
OL,15,Fdevelop.
OL,17,F"My instincts tell me that, in a
OL,18,Frecession, subbies (sub-postmasters)
OL,19,Fwith their hand in the till choose to
OL,20,Fblame the technology when they are
OL,21,Ffound to be short of cash."
