OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss accused staff of
OL,4,Chaving 'hands in the till', inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FSpeaking on Friday, Mr Cook told the
OL,8,Finquiry his email was "unacceptable"
OL,9,Fand one he will "regret for the rest
OL,10,Fof my life".
OL,12,F'I was unaware that the Post Office
OL,13,Fwere the prosecuting authority'
OL,15,FHe earlier admitted he did not realise
OL,16,Ffor a number of years that he was the
OL,17,Fhead of a prosecuting authority.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@dO]qD@QOUrD@KO]
