OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss accused staff of
OL,4,Chaving 'hands in the till', inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"I knew there were court cases but
OL,8,Fdidn't realise that the Post Office in
OL,9,Fabout two thirds of the cases had
OL,10,Finitiated the prosecution as opposed
OL,11,Fto the DPP or the police," he said.
OL,13,FMr Cook said: "Expressions were used
OL,14,Flike 'this is going to court'. I had
OL,15,Fassumed police and DPP were involved.
OL,16,FI shouldn't have assumed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@ZO]
