OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Cook replied: "That is my position,
OL,8,Fdefinitely."
OL,10,FThe former chief executive of the
OL,11,FRoyal Mail Group Adam Crozier, who
OL,12,Falso was quizzed at the inquiry,
OL,13,Fadmitted he did not have a "developed
OL,14,Funderstanding" of the Royal Mail
OL,15,Fcarried out prosecutions.
