OL,3,CEx-Post Office boss accused staff of
OL,4,Chaving 'hands in the till', inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe was asked: "Is the truth of the
OL,8,Fmatter that in your position you did
OL,9,Fnot have a developed understanding of
OL,10,Fthe extent to which Royal Mail
OL,11,Fprosecuted or the way in which things
OL,12,Fwere or were not carried into effect?"
OL,14,FMr Crozier responded: "I'm not a
OL,15,Flawyer. I would not claim it is my
OL,16,Farea of expertise."
OL,18,FHe also has expressed "huge regret"
OL,19,Fover the "tragic situation" for Post
OL,20,FOffice sub-postmasters and their
OL,21,Ffamilies during his time at Royal Mail.
