OL,7,FMr Castleton vs The Post Office
OL,9,FAhead of Mr Crozier's appearance at
OL,10,Fthe inquiry, Mr Cook was questioned
OL,11,Fabout the Post Office's case against
OL,12,Fsub-postmaster Lee Castleton.
OL,14,FMr Cook said he was "unaware" of the
OL,15,Forganisation's civil case against My
OL,16,FCastleton who was found to have a
OL,17,F#25,000 shortfall at his east
OL,18,FYorkshire branch.
OL,26,@vD@UOUvD@]O]
