OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe told the inquiry he did not ask
OL,8,Fquestions on the matter until he saw
OL,9,Fan article in Computer Weekly in May
OL,10,F2009, which was the first instance of
OL,11,Fthe scandal being picked up by the
OL,12,Fmedia.
OL,14,FHundreds of sub-postmasters are
OL,15,Fawaiting compensation, despite the
OL,16,Fgovernment announcing that those who
OL,17,Fhave had convictions quashed are
OL,18,Feligible for #600,000 payouts.
