OL,4,Chaving 'hands in the till', inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FIn recent months, The Post Office has
OL,8,Fcome under fire since the broadcast of
OL,9,FITV drama Mr Bates vs The Post Office,
OL,10,Fwhich put the Horizon scandal under
OL,11,Fthe spotlight.
OL,13,FMr Cook also went on to say he worked
OL,14,Fto boost the mood in the sub-
OL,15,Fpostmaster community, as he believed
OL,16,Fthey felt "unloved" when he came into
OL,17,Fthe role.
