OL,7,FHe said: "One of the first things I
OL,8,Fdid was establish a strong
OL,9,Frelationship with the chap who was
OL,10,Fthen the federations top guy and the
OL,11,Ftop team... Colin Baker.
OL,13,F"Then I started a programme of visits
OL,14,Fwhich in the end I did for the entire
OL,15,Fthree years and 10 months that I was
OL,16,Fthere... and I went randomly and
OL,17,Fvisited them."
